attributes.Long form description: The student is building a piece of furniture. He starts by attaching the legs to the middle shelf, and then screws the top shelf on. Finally, he tightens all the hex socket heads.

attributes.Transcription: Okay, we are performing the task  Knarrevik.

attributes.Action sentence: The student inspects the furniture regularly.

attributes.Transcription: Please start by assembling that one surface to the middle part of one leg.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the first leg to the middle shelf.

attributes.Transcription: Please don't tighten the screws completely yet.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the second leg to the middle shelf.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally
attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should continue assembling by putting the already assembled leg piece on the table and then continue assembling one leg to the part that is facing upwards.

attributes.Transcription: Please continue assembling by putting the already assembled leg piece on the table and then continue assembling one leg to the part that is facing upwards.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the third leg to the middle shelf.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student should turn the furniture such that the two assembled legs are both on the table.

attributes.Transcription: Please turn the furniture such that the two assembled legs are both on the table.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the fourth leg to the middle shelf.
The student screws the top shelf to the first leg.
The student screws the top shelf to the second leg.
The student screws the top shelf to the third leg.
The student screws the top shelf to the fourth leg.
The student tightens the hex socket heads of the first leg.

attributes.Transcription: Now, please make sure that all the screws are tightened.

attributes.Action sentence: The student tightens the hex socket heads on the second leg.
The student tightens the hex socket heads on the third leg.
The student tightens the hex socket heads on the fourth leg.

attributes.Transcription: Your task is over and you can stop recording.
